name: serde_json::de::de::Deserializer<R>::into_iter
doc: /// Turn a JSON deserializer into an iterator over values of type T.
code: pub fn into_iter<T>(self) -> StreamDeserializer<'de, R, T>
// This cannot be an implementation of std::iter::IntoIterator because
// we need the caller to choose what T is.

cond_chains.ret:
StreamDeserializer {
            de: self,
            offset,
            failed: false,
            output: PhantomData,
            lifetime: PhantomData,
        }
